refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
abstract public intmysql_xdevapi\BaseResult::getWarningsCount
Retorna o número de alertas gerados pela última operação. Especificamente, esses alertas são gerados pelo servidor MySQL.

  &reftitle.examples;

   Exemplo de mysql_xdevapi\RowResult::getWarningsCount


<?php
$session = mysql_xdevapi\getSession("mysqlx://user:password@localhost");

$session->sql("DROP DATABASE IF EXISTS foo")->execute();
$session->sql("CREATE DATABASE foo")->execute();
$session->sql("CREATE TABLE foo.test_table(x int)")->execute();

$schema = $session->getSchema("foo");
$table  = $schema->getTable("test_table");

$table->insert(['x'])->values([1])->values([2])->execute();

$res = $table->select(['x/0 as bad_x'])->execute();

echo $res->getWarningsCount();
?>


   &example.outputs.similar;


2
